Nelspruit Primary School has welcomed all its Grade One boys for 2023 on Wednesday. Most of these young boys were excited to be in big school and to meet their new classmates and teachers.  ALSO READ:Swimmers dive into action in Mbombela The principal, Werner van Tonder, said they only welcomed the boys on Wednesday to make sure they gave all the learners the attention they needed on their first day and to brief the parents in a small number. All the Grade One girls were welcomed today, December 12.           